        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Integrating Qwen3 TTS CustomVoice into your API involves setting up a server that handles text-to-speech requests. The model can be wrapped in a RESTful API using frameworks like FastAPI or Flask. Below is a Python example using FastAPI to create an endpoint that accepts text and returns audio in WAV format."
          }
