        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Deploying Qwen3 TTS CustomVoice in production requires careful consideration of scalability and reliability. Containerization with Docker is recommended to ensure consistent environments across development and production. The model can be deployed on Kubernetes for auto-scaling based on request load, with monitoring via Prometheus for latency and error rates."
