            "type": "text",
            "text": "A practical use case is integrating Qwen3 TTS CustomVoice into a customer service voice assistant. The custom voice feature allows brands to create a unique speaker identity, enhancing user engagement. With the 12Hz output, responses are generated quickly, reducing perceived wait times in interactive dialogues."
