        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "In this scenario, the API handles concurrent requests from multiple users, with each request specifying a voice ID for personalization. The low latency ensures that audio responses are delivered within 200ms, meeting the threshold for natural conversation flow. Additionally, the model's efficiency allows it to run on-premises, addressing data privacy concerns for sensitive industries like healthcare or finance."
