            "type": "text",
            "text": "When deploying Qwen3 TTS CustomVoice, you might encounter errors related to model loading or inference. Common issues include CUDA out-of-memory errors, which can be resolved by reducing batch size or using mixed-precision inference. The GitHub repository provides error codes and logs; for example, error code 1001 indicates insufficient VRAM."
